60
00:11:53,499 --> 00:11:55,099
But in the next twenty years,

61
00:11:55,898 --> 00:11:57,258
Lin Xirou only transformed

62
00:11:57,258 --> 00:11:58,619
a dozen humanoid Earth Fiends.

63
00:11:59,339 --> 00:12:00,219
Could it be

64
00:12:00,643 --> 00:12:02,819
her transformation into a human
was just a coincidence,

65
00:12:03,459 --> 00:12:05,499
and she's been trying
to replicate it ever since?

66
00:12:11,699 --> 00:12:13,619
It takes five hundred years

67
00:12:13,619 --> 00:12:14,979
