72
00:12:32,579 --> 00:12:34,099
Something rarer.

73
00:12:35,898 --> 00:12:37,339
I envy the older generation.

74
00:12:38,018 --> 00:12:39,099
Everything's simple.

75
00:12:40,018 --> 00:12:42,418
Easy to distinguish
between fiends and humans.

76
00:12:43,778 --> 00:12:44,898
But anyway,

77
00:12:45,178 --> 00:12:46,499
we can't be sure

78
00:12:46,499 --> 00:12:47,699
the records

79
00:12:47,699 --> 00:12:49,418
are complete.

80
00:12:55,499 --> 00:12:56,699
Contact me anytime.

81
00:12:57,938 --> 00:12:58,658
Thanks.

82
00:13:00,859 --> 00:13:02,499
Though there were more rational options,

83
00:13:03,538 --> 00:13:04,538
