124
00:18:07,738 --> 00:18:08,859
and become one of us

125
00:18:09,619 --> 00:18:10,779
is kind of help.

126
00:18:10,938 --> 00:18:12,458
Just like Locust you raised?

127
00:18:15,178 --> 00:18:16,059
In your eyes,

128
00:18:16,738 --> 00:18:18,458
any difference
between humans and fiends?

129
00:18:18,539 --> 00:18:19,299
Of course yes.

130
00:18:23,178 --> 00:18:25,059
Locust wasn't successfully tamed.

131
00:18:25,738 --> 00:18:27,299
I underestimated it.

132
00:18:27,648 --> 00:18:29,458
Sun Zhou has red threads
piercing his pupils,

133
00:18:29,978 --> 00:18:31,498
but he still remains his humanity.

134
00:18:31,619 --> 00:18:32,898
After being trained by Yu Rong,

135
00:18:32,978 --> 00:18:33,579
he could've...

136
00:18:33,579 --> 00:18:34,418
He's dead.

137
00:18:41,259 --> 00:18:42,339
Today in the mine,

138
00:18:42,691 --> 00:18:43,539
we saw an Earth Fiend

139
00:18:43,539 --> 00:18:45,779
that didn't fully transform
into human form.

140
00:18:48,418 --> 00:18:49,099
Indeed,

141
00:18:49,698 --> 00:18:50,859
he did become one of us

142
00:18:50,859 --> 00:18:51,978
and fought alongside us.

143
00:18:52,819 --> 00:18:55,138
But he couldn't live like us.

144
00:19:01,579 --> 00:19:02,418
You may leave.

145
00:19:02,738 --> 00:19:04,259
You are not needed here anymore.

146
00:21:59,619 --> 00:22:00,418
Miss Nie.

147
00:22:00,779 --> 00:22:01,619
I've searched.

148
00:22:01,779 --> 00:22:03,458
There's no Xicang instant noodles here.

149
00:22:03,619 --> 00:22:05,379
You usually don't eat
this kind of stuff.

150
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:06,898
Should I go out and look for some?

151
00:22:07,178 --> 00:22:07,898
Don't bother.

152
00:22:08,178 --> 00:22:09,339
These dried noodles will do.

153
00:22:10,019 --> 00:22:10,619
It's fine.

154
00:22:10,619 --> 00:22:11,938
Ms. Lu, you can go rest.

155
00:22:11,938 --> 00:22:12,898
I can handle it.

156
00:22:33,218 --> 00:22:34,019
Let me do it.

157
00:22:52,619 --> 00:22:53,498
Miss Nie.

158
00:22:54,059 --> 00:22:56,379
I've never seen you cook before.

159
00:22:57,938 --> 00:22:59,299
I'm worried he's starving.

160
00:23:03,555 --> 00:23:04,276
I'll do it.

161
00:23:58,243 --> 00:23:59,763
It's late now.

162
00:23:59,884 --> 00:24:01,203
I can only make something simple.

163
00:24:08,483 --> 00:24:10,763
How about I leave it by the door?

164
00:26:42,124 --> 00:26:42,844
Thanks.

165
00:26:48,804 --> 00:26:49,723
Get some rest.

166
00:27:09,324 --> 00:27:10,284
Over at the mine,

167
00:27:10,284 --> 00:27:11,276
Big Head and Shan Qiang

168
00:27:11,276 --> 00:27:13,003
temporarily restrained those underlings.

169
00:27:13,844 --> 00:27:15,203
The biggest gain this time

170
00:27:15,203 --> 00:27:17,283
is finding that Earth Fiend
down in the mine.

171
00:27:17,564 --> 00:27:21,683
So, that Earth Fiend down in the mine

172
00:27:23,084 --> 00:27:24,683
had already taken on human form

173
00:27:25,564 --> 00:27:28,084
but still retained some brutish nature.

174
00:27:28,683 --> 00:27:30,604
In the middle of a humanoid Earth Fiend

175
00:27:31,364 --> 00:27:33,564
and a primal Earth Fiend.

176
00:27:33,564 --> 00:27:34,164
Exactly.

177
00:27:34,644 --> 00:27:35,604
That mine

178
00:27:35,604 --> 00:27:37,164
was likely a transition spot

179
00:27:37,164 --> 00:27:39,084
for Earth Fiends freshly
transformed into humans.

180
00:27:39,644 --> 00:27:41,683
They need a transition spot

181
00:27:42,003 --> 00:27:44,203
